trans-unit.source: Exposes the data items in the collection of <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.Items*> in <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.GridView"></xref> types to [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)].
Creates a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.Peers.GridViewItemAutomationPeer"></xref> class.
The data item that is associated with this <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.Peers.GridViewItemAutomationPeer"></xref>.
The <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ListViewAutomationPeer"></xref> that is the parent of this <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.Peers.GridViewItemAutomationPeer"></xref>.

Gets the control type for the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.Items*> collection that is associated with this <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.Peers.GridViewItemAutomationPeer"></xref>. Called by <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.GetAutomationControlType*>.

Gets the collection of child elements of the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.Items*> collection that is associated with this <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.Peers.GridViewItemAutomationPeer"></xref>. Called by <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.GetChildren*>.

Gets the name of the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.Items*> collection that is associated with this <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.Peers.GridViewItemAutomationPeer"></xref>. Called by <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.GetClassName*>.
